WHERE TO FIND US
We are located off of Highway 192 in Kissimmee, Florida.
At the corner of Bass Road and Highway 192 (next to the Walmart), head south on Bass road until you reach Yowell Road (about 1 mile).  Take a right on Yowell Road and Great Oak RV Resort will be on your left.
